column2: "Repurposing a destroyed ARKS ship into a playground. He really has poor taste."
"I thought this would be entertaining, but there's nothing stimulating about this."
"I suppose it is my duty, but I have no direct obligation. This should be enough."
"Oh, it's you. To run into you in a place like this seems awfully unlikely."
"You're Dark Falz Elder, the one who took Master Gettemhart..."
